      </m:math>
    </equation><para id="import-auto-id1860430">(3) Calculate to find the frequency returning to the source: 2,500,649 Hz.</para><para id="import-auto-id2598726">
      <title>Solution for (c)</title>
    </para>
    <para id="import-auto-id3092028">(1) Identify knowns:</para>
    <list id="eip-378"><item>The beat frequency is simply the absolute value of the difference between <m:math><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>f</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mn>s</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub></m:mrow><m:mrow/></m:mrow></m:math> and <m:math><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>f</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>obs</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub></m:mrow><m:mrow/></m:mrow></m:math>, as stated in: <equation id="eip-id1164652542063"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>f</m:mi><m:mn>B</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">=</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">∣</m:mo><m:msub><m:mi>f</m:mi><m:mtext>obs</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">−</m:mo><m:msub><m:mi>f</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mn>s</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">∣</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mo>.</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></equation></item></list><para id="import-auto-id1596806">(2) Substitute known values:</para>
    <equation id="eip-627"><m:math>
        
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mrow>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mo stretchy="false">∣</m:mo>
                <m:mrow>
